Athens State University , located in Athens , Alabama , USA , is a two - year upper level university . Athens State is the only two - year upper level university in the state of Alabama . Thirty - three different majors are offered to junior and senior students . Athens State University began as the Athens Female Academy in 1822 . The Methodist Church took control of the institution in 1842 , changing the name to the Athens Female Institute . In 1931 the name was changed again to Athens College and it became coeducational . In 1974 the state of Alabama took control and the college became known as Athens State College . Later , in 1998 , Athens State College became Athens State University . 